      "span_text": "Problem 2 (Requirements classification  ): Given a set of requirements in natural language text R = {R 1 , . . . , R n }, the requirements classification problem asks to find a partition (L, H) of S such that L consists of all low-level requirements and H consists of all high-level requirements.",
